        X.Org Wii Remote Input Driver

This package includes an X.Org input driver for Nintendo Wii Remotes. It is
based on the xwiimote packages available at http://github.com/dvdhrm/xwiimote.

To install this driver use:
	./configure --prefix=/usr
	make
	make install

Please also copy the configuration file, otherwise the driver won't get loaded:
	cp 60-xorg-xwiimote.conf /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/

Please see the man-page of the driver for further information.

This driver was written by David Herrmann <dh.herrmann@googlemail.com>. For
license information see ./COPYING. If you have questions please don't hesitate
to contact me either per email or at:
	http://github.com/dvdhrm/xf86-input-xwiimote
